narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: It's fun! You'll get a good amount of personal attention and learn a lot more than you might think possible in a term.

As a short summary, I really enjoyed the course overall. I felt it was structured well and allowed us to learn the language at a practical level. I love Professor Vital! She is warm, funny, friendly, and incredibly intelligent. You can tell she has a sophisticated understanding of the nuances of the Portuguese language. This was very appreciated!
